entries.femaleVariant: Suicide, eh? Well, guess it wasn't that far-fetched.
Hey, V... Finally got the pics you sent.
Hey, V! Uh, listen, so, Randy's birthday's comin' up next week and Joss'll be making dinner on the twenty-uh--
Hey, V, listen, um... stupid question, but... d'you think you could bail me out?
V, hey.
V, hey. So, here's the thing.
Least, that's how half the people in Night City end up anyway... 'specially the good ones.
Jamie Sheen, my first partner back on the force, blew his brains out.
Didn't leave a note or anything, but I knew it was 'cause of how the top brass were handlin' things.
'Course, not like it changed much. 'Cept the fact we were down one more decent badge.
Anyway, hope you're in a better place, V.
Who'd've thought the Badlands could be so picturesque, right?
Maybe when things calm down 'round here a bit, I'll come 'n' visit, y'know, when Joss gets back on her feet.
Sometimes I think about what would've happened if we'd...
Eh, never mind. You've probably got better things to do than listen to me moan.
Good luck out there, V. Go where your heart takes you.
The twenty-first!
Right, right, right, the twenty-first. So uh... if you don't have any plans or somethin', or if you're in town and you're free, then--
Come on, it'll be fun!
Shut up, Dee!
Heh, well as you can see, it'd mean a lot to us.
Can we ride in your car?!
What did I just say?
Hey, cool it you two! Right now!
Uhh, OK... I'll call you later. See you soon, hopefully. And uh, stay outta trouble.
Last night I was sittin' at the bar just mindin' my own business, when some guy starts mouthin' off about the kids on the farm.
Sayin' that they must've enjoyed bein' hooked up like cows. That they had it comin'.
Of course, I told him to shut his fucking mouth or else.
Surprise, surprise, he didn't listen. So we took it outside and... well, you know what happens next.
They're holding me at the precinct in Little China â€“ you know where. Holler if you can help your ol' River out one last time. Thanks...
So I've been to every precinct in the city, every hospital, emergency room, every single rippderdoc...
Nobody knows what happened to you. It's like you're a ghost.
If that job went sour then I guess... I guess that's it, then.
But if everything went like it was supposed to, V... if you're alive... just call me, please. You owe me that much.
Anyway, uh... Bye, I guess.
Couple fellas from the fifth precinct busted a shop sellin' illegal iron.
Sawed-offs, stun guns, mustard gas cannisters...
Orders from on up were to blow it all to the ground, but then I thought... maybe there's a better way to use all this stuff. For a good cause.
I still remember what you did for us. For me and Randy.
This city needs more people like you... and I'm gonna make sure they're equipped.
This one's on me, V. See you around.
